# Contributors

This file lists all contributors to the Wi-Fi Location Changer project.

## Original Author

**Alex Rabinovich** <4alexr@gmail.com>
- GitHub: [@putchi](https://github.com/putchi)
- Original author and creator of the Wi-Fi Location Changer project
- Contributions:
  - Original project design and implementation
  - macOS Tahoe 26.0+ compatibility with Shortcuts app integration
  - Secure helper script implementation for location switching
  - Configuration UI development (SwiftUI app and shell-based tool)
  - Security improvements and vulnerability fixes
  - Documentation updates and installation improvements

